  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA11">
<l>kaṭainiṉ ṟamarar kaḻaṟoḻutu nāḷu</l>
<l>miṭainiṉṟa viṉpatta rāvar – puṭainiṉṟa</l>
<l>nīrōta mēṉi neṭumālē niṉṉaṭiyai</l>
<l>yārōta vallā ravar.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing in the entry, worshipping the ankleted [feet] of the immortals daily</l>
<l>they will be people with mediocre pleasures. Tall Māl</l>
<l>with the water-flood body who stands at the side,</l>
<l>who are those capable of reciting [verses] about your feet?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
